  "texts": [
    "To the best of our knowledge, OnSIDES is the only up-to-date and multi-national database of drug-label ADEs.",
    "It is also the only database that incorporates multi-ingredient drugs.",
    "The latest version of OnSIDES is publicly available online at https://github.com/tatonetti-lab/onsides.",
    "As new drugs are approved and drug labels are revised constantly, we have developed a computational pipeline to continually maintain and update the database quarterly and reflect the latest up-to-date knowledge available on ADEs, also available in the repository.",
    "In the OnSIDES database, we compile ADEs listed on drug labels for the general population."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}